rows.label: qev050105_MSG0001
rows.name:
You remained levelheaded throughout, yet at times
made moves that could only be called reckless.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0002
rows.name:
It is as if fire and water inhabited a single body.
I was wholly unable to read your attacks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0003
rows.name:
...No. The truth is that my own intentions were too
easily read. This is what my master tried to tell me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0004
rows.name:
I was always able to catch my opponents unaware
because Gi Ziordo was there to throw them off guard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0005
rows.name:
The same mindless violence I insulted was the very piece
missing from my own fighting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev050105_SEL0011
rows.name:
Suggest that Gi Ziorde rejoin
Gi Ziordo and train at his side.

rows.label: qev050105_JNK0020
rows.name: Disagree

rows.label: qev050105_SEL0021
rows.name:
Tell Gi Ziorde that he must address
his weaknesses by himself.

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0006
rows.name:
True. It may be something I would never find without
his aid.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0007
rows.name:
I thought I could do everything myself.
But fighting you has shown me the truth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0008
rows.name:
I need his heedless strength. If I am to grow strong,
it will be with him at my side.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0009
rows.name:
But I said many harsh things in our arguments,
and do not know the words to offer him now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0010
rows.name:
First, I must return to master Go Belg and thank him
for sending you to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0011
rows.name:
I would ask that you fight Gi Ziordo next.
For he is my greatest rival and strongest ally.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0012
rows.name:
Heh. That Wrothian is a wild beast.
You will not find him so simple to read.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050105_MSG0025
rows.name: For now, I beg your leave. Farewell.[ST:wait ]
